Bitbucket error :
git submodule add https://user_name@bitbucket.org/folder1/abc.git
I get the following error:
Missing or invalid credentials.
remote: Invalid credentials
fatal: Authentication failed for 'https://user_name@bitbucket.org/folder1/abc.git'

Solution :
Create an "app password" in bitbucket following the instructions https://community.atlassian.com/t5/Bitbucket-questions/Login-failed-due-to-incorrect-login-credentials-or-method/qaq-p/2195927
git clone https://user_name:abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvyxyz@bitbucket.org/folder1/abc.git submodules/cicd 

